readme: # react-native-typescript-snippets React Native Typescript snippets for Atom and atom-ide-ui. Installation ------------ Run the following terminal command: ``` apm install react-native-typescript-snippets ``` or Install via Atom package ``` Atom > Setting > Install > "Search packages" ``` Usage ----- The package provides two snippets * `rntsc` - React Native Typescript Class Component Boilerplate * `rntsp` - React Native Typescript Pure Component Boilerplate # Credits Credited to [aakashns/atom-react-native-snippets](https://github.com/aakashns/atom-react-native-snippets)
